Package: mmt-studio-core
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: MakeMyTechnology <release@makemytechnology.com>
Description: MMT Studio Core — 5G SA Core Network
 Single-binary 5G core with web GUI, real-time NGAP/NAS signalling,
 DPDK-accelerated UPF data plane, and SQLite subscriber DB.
 .
 Implements TS 24.501 (NAS), TS 38.413 (NGAP), TS 29.244 (PFCP),
 TS 33.501 (5G security), TS 35.205-207 (Milenage). Bundles a kernel
 SCTP NGAP transport, a cgo bridge to a DPDK 25.11 user-plane fast
 path, and a Chi/pongo2 web GUI.
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Makemytechnology/mmt-studio-core
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.35), libnuma1
